wmr 写道 <i>"政治讽刺小说《<a href="http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AB%E5%9B%9B">一九八四</a>》曾被拍成过<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nineteen_Eighty-Four_(TV_programme)">电视剧</a>、<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nineteen_Eighty-Four_(film)">电影</a>，被<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nineteen_Eighty-Four_in_popular_media">无数流行文化</a>引用。好莱坞公司决定<a href="http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/orwells-1984-film-adaptation-imagine-303003">再次拍成电影</a>。<a href="http://www.sfx.co.uk/2012/03/22/new-1984-film-in-development/">标题</a>是叫Nineteen Eighty-Four还是1984？观众会不会认为是古装剧？"</i>